          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " when they can’t truly afford them, but this guy took things to a whole other level. Based on his supposed wealth, and the claims that a Kuwaiti sovereign-wealth fund as well as the owner of a professional sports team were looking to invest in the hedge fun he was managing, Galles reportedly was able to get people to hand over their money without further questions.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
